lyrics:
[Verse]
Come as you are, don't hide your scars
In this world, you're shining stars
Let the music heal, let it carry you far
Embrace your truth, wherever you are

[Chorus]
Come as you are, oh, let your spirit fly
Find your strength, reach for the sky
Drown the doubts, let imagination soar high
Come as you are, let your fears say goodbye
